#: ../../source/using-api-interface.rst:221
msgid "So far we got an access token and created a template and a device based on it. In an actual deployment, the physical device would publish messages to dojot with all its attributes and their current values. For this tutorial we will publish MQTT messages by hand to the platform, emulating such physical device. For that, we will use mosquitto_pub and mosquitto_sub from `mosquitto`_."
